Schedule in brief

06 April

  • Crew arrives. Loads gear on R/V Daiber.

07 April

  • 06:00 Arrive at R/V Daiber
  • 06:30 - 16:20 eDNA sampling and mooring retrieval and redeployment for sites T-3C, T-2C, MBON5, MBON4, and A-5C.
  • MPT crew filming field work during cruise and will stop by Real-Time Whale Buoy (RTWB) site to film.

08 April

  • 06:00 Arrive at R/V Daiber
  • 06:30 - 13:20 eDNA sampling and mooring retrieval and redeployment for sites MBON3, MBON2, T-1C, and MBON1.
